    <title>glm_hermite()</title>
<indexterm><primary>glm_hermite</primary><secondary>bezier.h</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>bezier.h</primary><secondary>glm_hermite</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput><link linkend="_include_2cglm_2common_8h_1a132eda4e8b82a997831a6c857f7d26c1">CGLM_INLINE</link> float glm_hermite (float s, float p0, float t0, float t1, float p1)</computeroutput></para><para>

<para>cubic hermite interpolation </para>
</para>

<para>Formula: H(s) = P0*(2*s^3 - 3*s^2 + 1) + T0*(s^3 - 2*s^2 + s)<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>P1*(-2*s^3 + 3*s^2) + T1*(s^3 - s^2)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>

<para>similar result using matrix: H(s) = glm_smc(t, GLM_HERMITE_MAT, (vec4){p0, p1, c0, c1})</para>

<para>glm_eq(glm_smc(...), glm_hermite(...)) should return TRUE</para>

